  <brief_title>A Pilot Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of CigRx™ in Smokers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Active-Controlled, Crossover, Pilot Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CigRx™ Lozenge, a Non-Nicotine Non-Tobacco Dietary Supplement, in Daily Smokers in Temporarily Reducing the Desire to Smoke</official_title>
  <sponsors>
